  "description": "Maqam Sikah (maqam 3) — the neutral third, neither major nor minor, hovering between worlds. GENDY's random walk with very slow timeStep (0.02) means the stochastic path barely moves; each particle drifts like incense smoke. High gravity (0.8) draws notes toward the tonic but never resolves them. The prophecy hangs suspended in the air — neither spoken nor silent.",
